Package: SigPoisProcess
Type: Package
Title: Poisson process factorization for mutational signature analysis with genomic covariates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Alessandro", "Zito",
      email = "azito@hsph.harvard.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package implements the Poisson Process Factorization (PPF) method 
    for mutational signature analysis which also adds genomic covariates. 
    This package enables flexible analysis of mutational signatures using an inhomogeneous 
    Poisson point process where various genomic covariates (i.e. chromatin accessibility, 
    histone modifications, replication timing) shape the intensity function 
    along the genome via a log-linear model. 
